nodes.text: Tesche was a male Human who worked as a merchant during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. During the war, he operated a stall in the Alien Enclave Market of the city Voss-Ka on the planet Voss. Tesche wore brown and gray clothing while at his stall as well as a helmet. He had dark skin and brown eyes.

Tesche first appeared in Star Wars: The Old Republic, an MMORPG released by BioWare in 2011. In the game he serves as a Republic and Imperial commendations equipment vendor on the planet Voss. His location is also marked on a map in Prima Games' Star Wars: The Old Republic Explorer's Guide.
